      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i xDrive, finished in a stunning Bluestone Metallic over a pristine Black Dakota leather interior. This vehicle has been driven with care and serves as a testament to German engineering. The 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-6 engine provides effortless power and remains whisper-quiet at idle. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish; though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small hairline scratch near the trunk lid, the body is exceptionally straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, the cabin feels like a sanctuary. The leather seats are supple with no cracking or bolster wear, and the wood trim is free of sun-fading. All premium features, including the heated seats, head-up display, and the Harman Kardon surround sound system, are in perfect working order. This car has a clean title and has undergone a recent professional detailing and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, including a fresh oil service and new air filters. It is a turn-key luxury sedan ready for its next discerning owner.",
