    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2008 Porsche Cayman S featuring the legendary 3.4L mid-mounted flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus. This chassis delivers exceptional torsional rigidity and balanced weight distribution, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle for total engagement. The vehicle retains its factory-spec hydraulic power steering, providing the tactile feedback lost in newer EPS systems. Recent maintenance ensures the integrated dry-sump lubrication system and four-piston monobloc calipers are performing optimally. While showing honest signs of road use consistent with its age, the suspension geometry remains tight, and the engine pulls strongly through the entire rev range without hesitation. A mechanically robust example for the purist who prioritizes corner-exit stability and an evocative exhaust note.",
